{"tid":1635342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[更新] 全球最入屋國際文宣正式更新","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T22:44:15.000Z","uid":330837,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8f64753896b0ea5efbdc6a388286ba8f2eba62","tid":1635342,"uid":330837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:55.000Z","msg":"上文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626292/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626292/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下理:<br />\n<strong><ins>字體</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdY3bX5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdY3bX5.png&h=fb303d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETPaBpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETPaBpP.png&h=b6e18cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽到大家意見，將故事內文同title既字體改左，多謝絲打提供字型，感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，新增番用舊字體既option，見下圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwnziDc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwnziDc.png&h=4d00b017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋About同Settings 入邊既字體都統一番，希望大家睇得舒服d。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>UI</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18Xb5ih.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18Xb5ih.png&h=0c5be1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本呢頁太多唔同顏色，而家統一番。<br />\npublic opinion既表達分式都由成張card既顏色改做一條bar黎表達，原本既info button就remove左，d info放左出bar下邊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FtyzbL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FtyzbL.png&h=d1720b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為有意見指出同background撞左色，Navigation menu既圖都改左三幅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>新野</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzF1H47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzF1H47.png&h=e10b605a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 係About入邊加番twitter既navigation(暫時twitter得一個tweet，可以幫手retweet出去，無乜時間打太大段野，見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2. Update notification - 以後play store有update會係app到話俾大家知<br />\n3. Remove background song - 未通知dgx就用歌我要同大家道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(唔關佢地事，不過我要尊重番人地版權) 如果大家有咩music/song覺得岩放番入去，可以留言話我知<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Bugs fix</ins></strong><br />\n1. 炒左都要請sick leave<br />\n2. Hong kong park之後玩唔到落去<br />\n3. 延長解鎖成就個dialog既停留時間<br />\n4. 禁next button會crash既情況<br />\n5. Show ads會crash既情況<br />\n6. 玩到chater會crash既情況<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>未fix bug</ins></strong><br />\n1. Api response error - 有見到有人因為呢個問題而crash，但暫未trace到原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果真係經常出現呢個問題可以去setting開offline mode玩住先(100%唔炒，應該)<br />\n2. Difficulty唔清楚，我要研究下點樣改改個ui，期望跟埋下邊講既短期更新推出<br />\n<br />\n另外，關於play store上打名搵唔到一事聯絡左google，佢地既回覆如下:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqdKFRV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqdKFRV.png&h=a0867fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>未來</ins></strong><br />\n短期會推出challenge mode同埋一個chapter既更新，期望兩星期內完成，到時又麻煩大家陪我試bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(預計下次更新就係呢次，如果無大問題or我fix到個未fix bug)<br />\n長期會推出ios version，不過由於當初我做呢個project既時候都係邊做邊諗，所有logic都亂到七彩，需要不小時間去整理，打算番住part time黎做，所以預期係以多月計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Link</ins></strong><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spinnerofyarns.choicegame\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspinnerofyarns.choicegame&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=7d50514b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/spinnerofyarns.choicegame</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/of_yarns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fof_yarns&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=d2f1c2ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/of_yarns</a><br />\nEmail: spinnerofyarns.choicegame@gmail.com<br />\nDownload link: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=story.hk.hkmovement\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dstory.hk.hkmovement&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=dfa3afc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=story.hk.hkmovement</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>致謝</ins></strong><br />\n多謝大家熱烈支持，直至而家已經有~3500人download左，大慨有~30外國人(唔準確估計)。<br />\nemail左我既，我全部都有睇，多謝大家意見，不過我覆唔晒，唔好意思(我真係睇晒)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>最後</ins></strong><br />\nShare, comment, rate 同 update啦!<br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝街上既巴絲平安回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n距離成為國際入屋文宣仲有好遠路，光復香港，時代革命!"},{"pid":"8bf5b09002f7c684d43976e3fb0b61f3ac9a5f43","tid":1635342,"uid":330837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f0b0cda48bddaab9627e12517072c75d6704889","tid":1635342,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"The most popular forum in HK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b